Output demo/cli.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 760
Set Padding 18
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Hide
Type "cd /tmp/wqdemo && clear"
Enter
Show

Sleep 700ms
Type "waqwaq toc wiki | grep tree"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 1.8s

Type "waqwaq grep islands wiki"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 1.8s

Type "waqwaq cat speaking-tree wiki --render"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3.2s
